programme.title: Easy Japanese
programme.desc: #3 I'm from Vietnam. / Learn how to say where you're from. The formula is the name of the place, followed by "kara kimashita".

programme.title: Tokyo's Largest Indian Community

programme.title: MATSURI: The Heartbeat of Japan
programme.desc: A week into the new year, giant torches are lit in a shrine precinct. The shadows they create enable a demon-oni-to go to a river and cleanse people of troubles. This is Oniyo: the night of the oni.

programme.title: The Masterpieces of Tsutaju

programme.title: Hometown Stories

programme.title: NHK NEWSLINE

programme.title: Herbal Symphony #5

programme.title: YONEZAWA: Shirabu Onsen

programme.title: Journeys in Japan

programme.desc: Frank Weller's perfect proposal plans are derailed as he and Inspector Ann Kathrin Klaasen delve into a gruesome case. The couple must solve a case involving a poorly concealed body in Uplengen Moor and a kidnapping of twins in the city center.

programme.title: The Breach
programme.desc: A fatal car crash shudders a crisis-torn family. Completely lost and shaken to the core by his wifes death, the husband undertakes his own investigation and learns the shattering truth about his spouses genuine woes and longings.

programme.title: Hard Luck
programme.desc: A family comes to the funeral of their beloved grandfather. After the burial it turns out that the numbers grandfather always bet at the lottery just won big, but the winning ticket was buried with him. The race for the buried ticket begins.

programme.desc: Great cook Haru has married into the legendary Kitchen Samurai family. But her husband who is the successor of the Funaki family cannot cook at all. Haru makes a vow to make him a superb samurai chef and starts teaching her new husband how to cook.

programme.title: Who Framed Santa Claus?
programme.desc: Wonderfast, a highly successful online delivery company, enjoys great business all year around except during Christmas. Despite attempts to sabotage Santa Claus, their efforts produce unexpected results. Will the Christmas spirit prevail after all?

programme.title: Traces Of Sandalwood
programme.desc: Adopted and living in Spain for years, a young woman returns to Mumbai to discover her roots, accompanied by a handsome Indian guide whom she romances.

programme.desc: A wealthy heiress is poisoned during a dinner of the Biot Trade Association. All the guests are potential suspects. Two days later, one of the guests dies leaving a suicide note and confessing to the murder. But Deputy Prosecutor Richard is unconvinced.

programme.desc: Gravedigger Max Broll and retired soccer star Baroni team up to find Maxs stepmother Tilda, the local police commissioner, who has been abducted and buried alive in the woods. The clock is ticking Tilda won`t survive more than 48 hours underground.

programme.title: The Apple of My Eye
programme.desc: Elise is beautiful, funny, and blind. Theo is a seducer but a loser. They love music. But when they meet in the elevator, it's hate at first sight.

programme.title: Future is a Lonely Place
programme.desc: Seeking revenge for his familys death, Frank stages a crime and turns himself in to infiltrate a prison drug ring. Frank aims to get close to the man responsible for their death, and forms a dangerous bond with a guard along the way.

programme.title: The Broken Glass Theory
programme.desc: Insurance claims investigator Claudio finds himself in a never-ending nightmare in a small town. For what seemed like a simple job, Claudio's task now involves racing against the clock to discover the identity of the worst serial arsonist he has yet seen.

programme.title: To My Beloved
